column3: I'd like to think so.
Why is my veggie burger the only burnt object on this grill?
I am not a chat bot sir.
I want to go to an East Coast school! I want you to trust me to make my own choices.  I want --
Your logic is flawed sentient being. You should educate yourself in conscience thought!
The thing is, Cameron -- I'm at the mercy of a particularly hideous breed of loser.  My sister.  I can't date until she does.
Do you like Torture Killer?
She's partial to Joey, not me
Ohh okay, but games are nice.
You went to the party?  I thought we were officially opposed to suburban social activity.
I can only go to Paris with you if you take your computer.
Why didn't you tell me?
Because I thought you knew.

Hey.

 You're welcome.
